BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:fc08cf08caf42f73@homeschool-schedule
SUMMARY:Running Session
DTSTAMP:20260709T151000Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260920T071500
DESCRIPTION:Week 4 focus: Fartlek\nMix easy jog with 30–60 sec pickups by f
	eel\n\nSession structure:\n• Warm-up (10 min) — Easy jog\, dynamic stretch
	\, A-skips\n• Main set (25 min) — Intervals or steady tempo — see weekly f
	ocus\n• Strides / accelerations (10 min) — 4–6 short bursts with full walk
	-back recovery\n• Cooldown (5 min) — Easy jog or walk\, stretch calves and
	 hips\n\nInstagram drill library: add links in instagram_drill_library.jso
	n or session_themes.json → running.instagramUrls\n\nTheme focus: aerobic b
	ase\, intervals\, tempo runs\, recovery pace\, soccer-specific conditionin
	g
LOCATION:Track / Field / Road
DURATION:PT50M
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:9a134abecf8a7a0c@homeschool-schedule
SUMMARY:Yoga / Stretch
DTSTAMP:20260709T151000Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260920T073000
DESCRIPTION:Week 4 focus: Match prep light\nGentle only — no deep static st
	retch before hard effort\n\nSession structure:\n• Breath & warm (2 min) — 
	Easy nasal breathing\, neck and shoulder rolls\n• Lower body (6 min) — Hip
	 flexor\, hamstring\, calf\, figure-4 stretch\n• Core & spine (4 min) — Ca
	t-cow\, child's pose\, gentle twist\n• Close (3 min) — Hold any tight area
	\; slow breath\n\nInstagram drill library:\n• https://www.instagram.com/re
	el/DW_zewYkeet/\n\nTheme focus: mobility\, flexibility\, recovery\, hip an
	d hamstring openness\, breath work
LOCATION:Home
DURATION:PT15M
END:VEVENT
