BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:c52e75b65593be50@homeschool-schedule
SUMMARY:Shooting Session
DTSTAMP:20260709T151000Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20261017T071500
DESCRIPTION:Week 4 focus: Weak-foot shooting\nAll finishes non-dominant\; t
	echnique over power\n\nSession structure:\n• Warm-up (8 min) — Passing int
	o space\, light touches\n• Technique block (15 min) — Static ball — placem
	ent corners\n• Movement finishes (15 min) — Receive-pass-shoot or dribble-
	cut-shoot\n• Pressure reps (10 min) — Time limit or consecutive goals\n• C
	ooldown (2 min) — Easy passes\n\nInstagram drill library: add links in ins
	tagram_drill_library.json or session_themes.json → shooting.instagramUrls\
	n\nTheme focus: striking technique\, placement\, off the dribble\, first-t
	ime finishes
LOCATION:Training Field / Goal
DURATION:PT50M
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:5346150d74b5c3a0@homeschool-schedule
SUMMARY:Yoga / Stretch
DTSTAMP:20260709T151000Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20261017T073000
DESCRIPTION:Week 4 focus: Match prep light\nGentle only — no deep static st
	retch before hard effort\n\nSession structure:\n• Breath & warm (2 min) — 
	Easy nasal breathing\, neck and shoulder rolls\n• Lower body (6 min) — Hip
	 flexor\, hamstring\, calf\, figure-4 stretch\n• Core & spine (4 min) — Ca
	t-cow\, child's pose\, gentle twist\n• Close (3 min) — Hold any tight area
	\; slow breath\n\nInstagram drill library:\n• https://www.instagram.com/re
	el/DW_zewYkeet/\n\nTheme focus: mobility\, flexibility\, recovery\, hip an
	d hamstring openness\, breath work
LOCATION:Home
DURATION:PT15M
END:VEVENT
