DESCRIPTION:Week 1 focus: Easy aerobic\n30–40 min comfortable pace — build 
	base\, conversation effort\n\nSession structure:\n• Warm-up (10 min) — Eas
	y jog\, dynamic stretch\, A-skips\n• Main set (25 min) — Intervals or stea
	dy tempo — see weekly focus\n• Strides / accelerations (10 min) — 4–6 shor
	t bursts with full walk-back recovery\n• Cooldown (5 min) — Easy jog or wa
	lk\, stretch calves and hips\n\nInstagram drill library: add links in inst
	agram_drill_library.json or session_themes.json → running.instagramUrls\n\
	nTheme focus: aerobic base\, intervals\, tempo runs\, recovery pace\, socc
	er-specific conditioning
