BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:09ca4977bba19cef@homeschool-schedule
SUMMARY:Shooting Session
DTSTAMP:20260709T151000Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20261205T071500
DESCRIPTION:Week 3 focus: One-touch finishes\nWall or partner feed\; adjust
	 body early\n\nSession structure:\n• Warm-up (8 min) — Passing into space\
	, light touches\n• Technique block (15 min) — Static ball — placement corn
	ers\n• Movement finishes (15 min) — Receive-pass-shoot or dribble-cut-shoo
	t\n• Pressure reps (10 min) — Time limit or consecutive goals\n• Cooldown 
	(2 min) — Easy passes\n\nInstagram drill library: add links in instagram_d
	rill_library.json or session_themes.json → shooting.instagramUrls\n\nTheme
	 focus: striking technique\, placement\, off the dribble\, first-time fini
	shes
LOCATION:Training Field / Goal
DURATION:PT50M
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:8e65260a7dc9a5cb@homeschool-schedule
SUMMARY:Yoga / Stretch
DTSTAMP:20260709T151000Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20261205T073000
DESCRIPTION:Week 3 focus: Hip focus\nRunners' hips — pigeon\, lizard\, 90/9
	0\n\nSession structure:\n• Breath & warm (2 min) — Easy nasal breathing\, 
	neck and shoulder rolls\n• Lower body (6 min) — Hip flexor\, hamstring\, c
	alf\, figure-4 stretch\n• Core & spine (4 min) — Cat-cow\, child's pose\, 
	gentle twist\n• Close (3 min) — Hold any tight area\; slow breath\n\nInsta
	gram drill library:\n• https://www.instagram.com/reel/DW_zewYkeet/\n\nThem
	e focus: mobility\, flexibility\, recovery\, hip and hamstring openness\, 
	breath work
LOCATION:Home
DURATION:PT15M
END:VEVENT
