BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:67867258194d4eef@homeschool-schedule
SUMMARY:Running Session
DTSTAMP:20260709T151000Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20261227T071500
DESCRIPTION:Week 2 focus: Interval repeats\n6–8 × 2 min hard / 2 min jog — 
	quality over volume\n\nSession structure:\n• Warm-up (10 min) — Easy jog\,
	 dynamic stretch\, A-skips\n• Main set (25 min) — Intervals or steady temp
	o — see weekly focus\n• Strides / accelerations (10 min) — 4–6 short burst
	s with full walk-back recovery\n• Cooldown (5 min) — Easy jog or walk\, st
	retch calves and hips\n\nInstagram drill library: add links in instagram_d
	rill_library.json or session_themes.json → running.instagramUrls\n\nTheme 
	focus: aerobic base\, intervals\, tempo runs\, recovery pace\, soccer-spec
	ific conditioning
LOCATION:Track / Field / Road
DURATION:PT50M
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:dc82fae5985059c5@homeschool-schedule
SUMMARY:Yoga / Stretch
DTSTAMP:20260709T151000Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20261227T073000
DESCRIPTION:Week 2 focus: Morning mobility\nShorter holds\, more movement b
	etween poses\n\nSession structure:\n• Breath & warm (2 min) — Easy nasal b
	reathing\, neck and shoulder rolls\n• Lower body (6 min) — Hip flexor\, ha
	mstring\, calf\, figure-4 stretch\n• Core & spine (4 min) — Cat-cow\, chil
	d's pose\, gentle twist\n• Close (3 min) — Hold any tight area\; slow brea
	th\n\nInstagram drill library:\n• https://www.instagram.com/reel/DW_zewYke
	et/\n\nTheme focus: mobility\, flexibility\, recovery\, hip and hamstring 
	openness\, breath work
LOCATION:Home
DURATION:PT15M
END:VEVENT
