BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:9a8e21f0d6d1d6f4@homeschool-schedule
SUMMARY:Shooting Session
DTSTAMP:20260709T151000Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20270213T071500
DESCRIPTION:Week 1 focus: Placement\nInside foot — low corners\, same techn
	ique every rep\n\nSession structure:\n• Warm-up (8 min) — Passing into spa
	ce\, light touches\n• Technique block (15 min) — Static ball — placement c
	orners\n• Movement finishes (15 min) — Receive-pass-shoot or dribble-cut-s
	hoot\n• Pressure reps (10 min) — Time limit or consecutive goals\n• Cooldo
	wn (2 min) — Easy passes\n\nInstagram drill library: add links in instagra
	m_drill_library.json or session_themes.json → shooting.instagramUrls\n\nTh
	eme focus: striking technique\, placement\, off the dribble\, first-time f
	inishes
LOCATION:Training Field / Goal
DURATION:PT50M
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:2f7e35f16ee23560@homeschool-schedule
SUMMARY:Yoga / Stretch
DTSTAMP:20260709T151000Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20270213T073000
DESCRIPTION:Week 1 focus: Post-training recovery\nLonger holds after hard s
	essions\n\nSession structure:\n• Breath & warm (2 min) — Easy nasal breath
	ing\, neck and shoulder rolls\n• Lower body (6 min) — Hip flexor\, hamstri
	ng\, calf\, figure-4 stretch\n• Core & spine (4 min) — Cat-cow\, child's p
	ose\, gentle twist\n• Close (3 min) — Hold any tight area\; slow breath\n\
	nInstagram drill library:\n• https://www.instagram.com/reel/DW_zewYkeet/\n
	\nTheme focus: mobility\, flexibility\, recovery\, hip and hamstring openn
	ess\, breath work
LOCATION:Home
DURATION:PT15M
END:VEVENT
