BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:c9e3eb2a7b3b2695@homeschool-schedule
SUMMARY:Running Session
DTSTAMP:20260709T151000Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20270425T071500
DESCRIPTION:Week 3 focus: Tempo run\n15–20 min comfortably hard — steady\, 
	no sprinting\n\nSession structure:\n• Warm-up (10 min) — Easy jog\, dynami
	c stretch\, A-skips\n• Main set (25 min) — Intervals or steady tempo — see
	 weekly focus\n• Strides / accelerations (10 min) — 4–6 short bursts with 
	full walk-back recovery\n• Cooldown (5 min) — Easy jog or walk\, stretch c
	alves and hips\n\nInstagram drill library: add links in instagram_drill_li
	brary.json or session_themes.json → running.instagramUrls\n\nTheme focus: 
	aerobic base\, intervals\, tempo runs\, recovery pace\, soccer-specific co
	nditioning
LOCATION:Track / Field / Road
DURATION:PT50M
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:156e883c2093dd94@homeschool-schedule
SUMMARY:Yoga / Stretch
DTSTAMP:20260709T151000Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20270425T073000
DESCRIPTION:Week 3 focus: Hip focus\nRunners' hips — pigeon\, lizard\, 90/9
	0\n\nSession structure:\n• Breath & warm (2 min) — Easy nasal breathing\, 
	neck and shoulder rolls\n• Lower body (6 min) — Hip flexor\, hamstring\, c
	alf\, figure-4 stretch\n• Core & spine (4 min) — Cat-cow\, child's pose\, 
	gentle twist\n• Close (3 min) — Hold any tight area\; slow breath\n\nInsta
	gram drill library:\n• https://www.instagram.com/reel/DW_zewYkeet/\n\nThem
	e focus: mobility\, flexibility\, recovery\, hip and hamstring openness\, 
	breath work
LOCATION:Home
DURATION:PT15M
END:VEVENT
