BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:c0d6ebcb53ca14eb@homeschool-schedule
SUMMARY:Shooting Session
DTSTAMP:20260709T151000Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20270612T071500
DESCRIPTION:Week 2 focus: Off the dribble\nCut inside\, laces drive\, 6–12 
	yards out\n\nSession structure:\n• Warm-up (8 min) — Passing into space\, 
	light touches\n• Technique block (15 min) — Static ball — placement corner
	s\n• Movement finishes (15 min) — Receive-pass-shoot or dribble-cut-shoot\
	n• Pressure reps (10 min) — Time limit or consecutive goals\n• Cooldown (2
	 min) — Easy passes\n\nInstagram drill library: add links in instagram_dri
	ll_library.json or session_themes.json → shooting.instagramUrls\n\nTheme f
	ocus: striking technique\, placement\, off the dribble\, first-time finish
	es
LOCATION:Training Field / Goal
DURATION:PT50M
END:VEVENT
